stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Creating: Create Instance
    Creating --> Running: Provisioned
    
    Running --> Paused: Pause (Manual or Auto)
    Paused --> Running: Resume
    
    Running --> Resizing: Resize
    Resizing --> Running: Complete
    
    Running --> Updating: Software Update
    Updating --> Running: Complete
    
    Running --> Restoring: Restore Snapshot
    Restoring --> Running: Complete
    
    Running --> Deleting: Delete
    Paused --> Deleting: Delete
    Deleting --> [*]: Terminated
    
    note right of Creating
        Neo4j provisions:
        - Compute resources
        - Storage
        - Network config
    end note
    
    note right of Running
        Instance is:
        - Accepting connections
        - Processing queries
        - Incurring costs
    end note
    
    note right of Paused
        Instance is:
        - Not accepting connections
        - Data preserved
        - No compute costs
    end note

